{"tid":827071,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【山竹風災】港珠澳大橋人工島有冇損毀？《蘋果》航拍畀你睇","createTime":"2018-09-18T16:26:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-19T10:42:03.000Z","uid":66923,"like":1,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"215e81c1d9a39a4ad8f6240fc071c399112a652b","tid":827071,"uid":66923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T16:26:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180918/58696775\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180918%2F58696775&d=8w4Rztlu%2FXTBsuJOe601sHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=1a77f29f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180918%2F58696775&h=f526640e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180918/58696775</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n千億跨境基建港珠澳大橋通車在即，特首林鄭月娥今稱，港珠澳大橋及高鐵香港段，經歷今次颱風「山竹」仍安然無恙，從基建角度是經得起考驗，感到安慰。兩項基建的安全一向備受公眾質疑，《蘋果》今往港珠澳大橋及其連接的人工島視察，從航拍片段可見，人工島似乎與今年4月所拍攝到的沒有太大分別，防波堤的扭工字塊（消波塊）仍像被海浪沖散。<br />\n<br />\n不過，新華社昨天報道指，據其記者向大橋管理局了解，有大橋個別室外燈具損壞、有房間門窗出現滲漏。而橋樑及隧道結構完好，主要設施功能正常，東西人工島扭工字塊防浪效果良好、狀態正常。報道又指，山竹來襲時，大橋管理局啟動了Ⅰ級響應、有83人員在東人工島、西人工島、收費樓、救援樓等設施值守。<br />\n<br />\n大橋管理局又透露山竹來襲時，錄得最大風速為55m/s，風力相當於16級。報道又指港珠澳大橋的顫振臨界風速一般為96.4m/s至大於150m/s，這說明港珠澳大橋具備足夠的抗風能力。<br />\n《蘋果》今年4月獨家揭發，港珠澳大橋人工島逾千個總重量逾千噸的消波塊疑被沖散捲入海中。內地的港珠澳大橋管理局當時回應稱，是刻意把部份消波塊「隨機」放到海中以形成潛堤，否認有安全問題，惟多名工程師均表明不相信當局說法。"},{"pid":"42eee13d42be2d12d7e910c2fc4906ca5037fbf2","tid":827071,"uid":104017,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T16:27:56.000Z","msg":"人在做，天在看<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c1fdcab8d8e7a6c5b67d0b098a117a295d00aa4","tid":827071,"uid":16676,"like":20,"dislike":4,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T16:55:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/19/005021_cb16d8a29f014bb2d09a59f98173ecf2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F19%2F005021_cb16d8a29f014bb2d09a59f98173ecf2.png&h=5abb2c95&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/19/005022_21679b58d4d4dac868a36f3d6dce7fc2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F19%2F005022_21679b58d4d4dac868a36f3d6dce7fc2.png&h=c3e35430&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解有時1架車, 有時2架車<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n工程車點解泊沙地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n可能係影左兩個人工島, <br />\n但會唔會咁巧合其中一架車個泊位置兩個島都係固定係中間(沙地)<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nd CG 真係好奇妙, 唔好計個陰影位先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">總結:好撚假</span>"},{"pid":"329dc1de6eb3e38414ad7ff81fdc7aab0f0a5bd7","tid":827071,"uid":140127,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T02:27:13.000Z","msg":"睇咗cm度d人係飛機影既相，見到防波堤既損毀比條片入面嚴重，加上打完風後竟然仍然乾淨到咁，防波堤上面一舊垃圾發泡膠都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係好難唔懷疑條片既真確性。究竟有冇其他方法自己去查驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2a7c413537e72226772a74754f12981df970b21","tid":827071,"uid":64191,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T02:29:42.000Z","msg":"CG？"},{"pid":"81fe4a2f847c182fbb68890ff8c0436b16fdc5ed","tid":827071,"uid":140127,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T02:33:35.000Z","msg":"呢單嘢真係要push，若然造假屬實，已經唔係以前報導偏頗、選擇性報導既層次，而係堂堂正正既發放假消息、擅改事實！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  仲要係出自一向「反建制」既蘋果，簡直係1984 既Ministry of Truth 真理部咁，諗起都恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi